Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:58.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,After getting through the busy period from October\Nuntil now, we all wanted to get out into the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:03.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so c-c-c-cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:07.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose idea was it to ride on this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:08.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My ears are gonna fall off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:10.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:17.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandma told me that it was fun to ride when\Nshe came to the city from the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:20.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But... sorry. She did that during spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:25.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since we came all this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:28.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Things like this are sometimes fun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:30.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
