Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:38.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really going to eat all this in two hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:40.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, you might be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:43.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:45.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:47.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This receipt is so long! And the total is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:51.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Buying a lot of things at the convenience store can get expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:55.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you said that all we needed were hard-boiled\Neggs when I offered to make a boxed lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:01.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If they say that, maybe we should've made a boxed lunch, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:02.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:03.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:07.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Making the girls do so much work is rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I love hard-boiled eggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:14.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too! I'm happy with just these!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:16.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:20.19,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if we had let them make the boxed lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:23.49,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,...who knows what kind of experimental\Nboxed lunch would have popped up.
