Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:38.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun, let's have some hard-boiled eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:40.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right, Mayama-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:28.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's pretty close.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:33.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't usually get a chance to see airplanes from below.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:37.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Haneda Airport must be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:39.44,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Haneda {\be1\3c&H000000&}is the original international Tokyo airport,\Nbefore Narita was built in the late 80s.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:39.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of them flying by.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know, Takemoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:47.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,About 700 airplanes take off from and land at Haneda each day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:48.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,700?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:53.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That adds up to one every two minutes,\Neven if the airport operates all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:58.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That many people use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:00.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Going far away and coming from far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:03.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone must be busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:05.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takemoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:08.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:10.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, nothing happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:12.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez. What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:15.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you've been acting depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:16.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:19.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, really, there's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:20.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:24.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since just before the Hamabi Festival, to be precise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been down ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:33.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen with Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:39.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're terrible! I was saving that for last, Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:41.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already eaten it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:46.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ew! Don't regurgitate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:51.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So Morita-san gave her a broach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:07.11,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kazarazu ni kimi no subete to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:07.11,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now it feels like I can become one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:04.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So... what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:07.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do? Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:10.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're totally willing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:16.58,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}mazariaesou sa ima sara ne
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:16.58,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...with everything that's you without embellishments.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:16.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like this winning and losing stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you won't go into the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:23.83,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}koibito to yoberu jikan wo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:23.83,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I kept the time we could call each other lovers...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:22.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just forfeiting the game itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:26.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you trying to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:34.97,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}hoshizuna hitotsu ni tojikometa
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:34.97,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...in a grain of sea sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Takemoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:31.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been almost two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:34.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Two years?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:38.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Two years since you came to like Hagu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:43.60,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kotoba ja naku rizumu wa tsuzuku
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:43.60,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not words, but rhythm continues...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:40.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-W-W-Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:44.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've known it since day one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:51.65,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}futari ga mada deau mae kara no
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:51.65,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...ever since before we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:52.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:08:00.41,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kurikaesu nami no koe tsumetai hi to samayou
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:08:00.41,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hearing the voice of the repeating wave we wander with the cold sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Two years is a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:07.42,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}furueru kata wo daite
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:07.42,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Holding your shivering shoulders...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:07.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've been by her side this whole time,\Nand you've become great friends with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:10.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with a difficult girl like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:13.26,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}dokoni mo modoranai
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:13.26,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...I won't go back to anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:18.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All the important things like the trust\Nyou've been building up with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:20.27,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"kitto mada owaranai yo" to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:20.27,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Saying, "I'm sure it won't end"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:24.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you abandoning them all just because you don't want to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:29.82,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}sakana ni narenai sakana to ka
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:29.82,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...or telling the tale of the fish that couldn't become a fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:33.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something you should give up on so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:48.29,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ikutsu mono tsukuribanashi de kokoro no ichibu wo uruoshite
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:48.29,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...you were wetting a part of my heart with the numerous fairy tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:37.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try to remember the time you've spent with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:56.84,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kono umi wa bokura no umi sa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:56.84,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This ocean is our ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:09:05.23,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kakusareta sekai to tsunagu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:09:05.23,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It connects us to a hidden world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:34.06,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}namariiro ni kagayaku kono umi wa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:34.06,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This ocean with its metallic glimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:43.23,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kakusareta...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:43.23,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A hidden...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:51.61,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kotoba ja naku...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:51.61,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not words...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:10:01.08,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}futari ga mada deau mae kara no
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:10:01.08,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We wander along with the cold sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:09.72,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}konkuriito ni shimikomu tsumetai hi to samayou
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:09.72,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...that has been staining the concrete since before we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:16.97,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}furueru kata wo daite
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:16.97,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Holding your shivering shoulders...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:23.19,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}doko ni mo modoranai
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:23.19,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...I won't go back to anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:40.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takemoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:47.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:52.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...think I'm going to puke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.68,0:10:54.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're seasick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:10:58.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please get a hold of yourself, Mayama-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:16.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:19.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a plastic bag. Here, drink this cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:21.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:24.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so high maintenance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:27.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:34.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:37.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:46.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet he thinks he's reliable when\Nhe's actually hopeless and pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you still like a guy like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:28.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama told me "no", but I can't stop liking him that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:42.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And feelings like these don't just slip away and\Ndisappear simply because I can't date him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:48.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:50.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:53.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:58.34,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:01.22,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:07.19,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who should be embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:10.23,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm the one who's uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:21.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your patience, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:26.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This vessel will arrive at the Kasai Seaside Park shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:46.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.27,0:13:49.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's nobody around as far as I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:51.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really one of the 23 Tokyo districts?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:59.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is beyond being a park. It's more like a grassland.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:05.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks even more pathetic because\Nit just opened and is still well kept.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:09.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I sure am glad we came. It was a great choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:17.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This nice, empty pocket formed because most\Npeople decide to hang around one stop away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:22.18,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\fs32\b0\fscx80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\bord1\shad0\3c&H545C8D&\c&H97A0BC&\pos(188,132)}squeeze
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:22.18,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\fs32\b0\fscx80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\bord1\shad0\pos(43,203)\c&H97A0BC&\3c&H4B4B94&}squeeze
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:21.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is seriously recommended for a date. Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:25.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mayama, why are you acting so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:29.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you always so fanatical?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:35.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the middle of the grassland is an oddly huge ferris wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:41.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That ferris wheel is the second largest in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:43.66,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\shad0\bord2\be1\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fscy80\fs60\fsp-3\pos(585,186)\3c&HDEDEDE&\c&H7176A4&}{\c&H6F74A2&}Second{\c&H51554A&} Largest in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:43.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure seems happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's something wrong here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:52.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We walk and walk, but it's not getting any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:54.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it running away from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:57.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it just be a mirage?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm gonna ride it no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:07.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ayu, could it be that they're closed today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:11.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that wheel even moving? It looks stopped to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.60,0:15:12.73,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,50)\frz6\be1\bord0.1\fscy90\shad0\fs23\i1\pos(447,430)\3c&HEAE0DB&\c&HE9D5CD&}Ferris Wheel
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:26.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing is extraordinarily huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:28.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:29.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like it might show up in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:32.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's open!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:34.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! How much is the ticket?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:34.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,700 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been on a ferris wheel in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:39.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:41.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:43.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...is a four-seater.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:49.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ride it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:47.97,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz27\shad0\bord2\fscy90\be1\fs24\c&HF2F0FB&\3c&H8B84B5&\pos(390,396)}Interest?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:48.60,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz27\shad0\bord2\fscy90\be1\fs24\c&HF2F0FB&\3c&H8B84B5&\pos(390,396)}Interest?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:49.22,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,150)\frz27\shad0\bord2\fscy90\be1\fs24\c&HF2F0FB&\3c&H8B84B5&\pos(390,396)}Interest?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:49.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAlsina Ultrajada\frz30\bord1\be1\fscy80\i1\shad0\fs44\pos(428,432)\c&H8C8EC5&\3c&H5A6073&}In love
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:50.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAlsina Ultrajada\frz30\bord1\be1\fscy80\i1\shad0\fs44\pos(428,432)\c&H8C8EC5&\3c&H5A6073&}In love
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:53.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:16:00.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just that I don't really like high places.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:02.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess I'll pass this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:04.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:05.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all getting on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:08.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. How long does it take to go around?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:09.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seventeen minutes, it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.16,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Seventeen minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:15.67,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means that once I'm in the gondola...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:19.59,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll be in a closed-off space for 17 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:21.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan, let's go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:22.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:27.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mayama-san, why don't the three\Nguys go on a humble ride together?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:33.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:34.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:37.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You two should get plenty of chatting done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:41.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a thoughtful person!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:41.90,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\fnAlsina Ultrajada\b0\fsp3\fscy80\shad0\fs90\move(2,798,2,-245)\3c&H5B605C&\c&H8D76AF&}Thoughtful Person
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:49.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)\bord1.6\shad0\fscy95\fsp-1\fs28\3c&H404039&\c&HFFFFFF&}(You shouldn't get on so recklessly. You'll get scolded.)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:51.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, that does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:04.92,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,It's awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:09.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:14.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't we all just smile all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:22.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I didn't understand why ferris wheels existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:26.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They were just sluggish and went high up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:30.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I got bored with it after only one ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:33.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The roller coaster and the loop slider...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:37.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I only paid attention to the thrilling rides.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:39.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:44.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:55.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ferris wheels are for slowly cutting across\Nthe sky with the person you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:18:01.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And maybe saying things like, "Isn't this a little scary?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.40,0:18:03.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:19.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:21.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:27.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)\bord1.6\shad0\fscy95\fsp-1\fs26\3c&H404039&\pos(424,135)}(This is dangerous, so please don't ever copy it. You'll\Ncause the wheel to have an emergency stop.)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:27.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:34.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:35.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:37.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:47.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I apologized properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:45.94,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\frz72\fscy150\fscx120\fs36\bord1.5\be1\shad0\b1\fnAlsina Ultrajada\move(418,263,423,219)\c&H6A514A&\3c&H413A34&}Gaaaan
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:52.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've seen you apologize, Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.95,0:18:52.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:54.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude! Takemoto, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:59.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I thought, "Could it be?"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:03.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it became funny and I loosened up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:09.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that Morita-san is also uneasy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:11.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...just like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:18.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun, Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:22.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's almost time for our ship. Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:23.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:26.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:28.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:34.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what Yamada-san and Mayama-san talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:37.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:40.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:45.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I don't know where all of us are headed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:52.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.51,0:19:53.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the boat is all ours again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:17.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:23.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:30.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a few years ago, we didn't even know\Nwhat the others of us looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:37.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But now we all spend time together like it's a matter of fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:42.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...watch the sunset together, and say\Nthings like, "Isn't this beautiful?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:47.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about stuff like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.23,0:20:49.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.07,0:20:54.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The sunset I see as I stand next to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:58.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...is so beautiful that it aches my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:00.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:10.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As we carry on like that, a new year is approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:28.02,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}akanai mabuta kosutte mieru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:28.02,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I rub my heavy eyelids to reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:33.15,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}pastel moyou no mirai ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:33.15,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}A future in the shape of pastels
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:40.28,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}chiribamerareta kigou o tadoru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:40.28,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I follow the scattered symbols
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:44.37,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}taguri yoseta hyoujou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:44.37,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}As my expressions were pulled in closer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:50.13,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}nee nandakke sagashiteita mono
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:50.13,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Say, what was it that we were looking for again?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.67,0:21:53.21,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}are wa soune itsudakke
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.67,0:21:53.21,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}That's right, exactly when were those days
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.17,0:22:00.59,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}bokura ga inryoku ni sakarai nagara deatta koro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.17,0:22:00.59,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}When we used to meet, denying the attraction\Nthat was forming between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:06.52,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sore ga waltz no you dane fushigi sa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:06.52,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}It's like a waltz, isn't it? It's quite marveling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:12.73,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sasayaku youna komorebi no kousaten de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:12.73,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}We paint away sceneries
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.90,0:22:18.95,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}futari waltz no youni ne mawari nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.90,0:22:18.95,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}As we waltz and spin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:25.08,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}egaki dashite yuku mono
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:25.08,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}Where the whispering sunlight falls through the trees and meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.83,0:22:34.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Flung around by love.
